  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Photographer / Videographer Wanted",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for a <strong>Photographer / Videographer</strong> to create high-quality photo and video content for marketing and digital platforms.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan, shoot, and edit photos and videos for social media, website, ads, events, and campaigns</p></li><li><p>Handle both studio and on-location shoots</p></li><li><p>Edit videos (cut, color, sound) and retouch photos</p></li><li><p>Work with the marketing team on concepts and ideas</p></li><li><p>Manage and take care of camera and production equipment</p></li><li><p>Organise media files and footage</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Relevant experience with a <strong>portfolio</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to shoot and edit photos & videos</p></li><li><p>Familiar with editing software (Premiere Pro / Final Cut / Lightroom / Photoshop, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Good understanding of lighting, framing, and storytelling</p></li><li><p>Able to manage multiple projects and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Creative, detail-oriented, and a team player</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply with your portfolio </strong><br /><strong>Email : Andrewechua6@yahoo.com.sg</strong><br /><strong>Whatappt : 8323 4406</strong></p>",
